item.title: CVE-2024-36267|2024-05-30T05:33:45.258Z -- Kontron -- Redmine DMSF Plugin
item.description: Path traversal vulnerability exists in Redmine DMSF Plugin versions prior to 3.1.4. If this vulnerability is exploited, a logged-in user may obtain or delete arbitrary files on the server (within the privilege of the Redmine process).
